ement one, and only one of the methods. Methods on this protocol will not be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"called on main thread, they will be called on the caller’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"requestQueue"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNImageSource":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNImageSource","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnimagesource","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNImageSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a content source that is used for a georeferenced raster"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image to be shown on the map. The georeferenced image scales and rotates as the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user zooms and rotates the map. Images may also be used as icons or patterns"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in a style layer. To register an image for use as an icon or pattern,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/setImage:forName:","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method. To configure a point"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s image, use the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class."}],"title":"MLNImageSource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNImageSource","kind":"identifier"}]}}}